This paper involves statistical analysis and mathematical modeling to investigate the underlying consumer and merchant behavior in the daily deals marketplace. It also leverages a large dataset to evaluate various hypotheses. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
